data.description: Home for the Holidays! Immaculate Mountain View home! Beautifully Remodeled 3 bed/2 bath with your own private Suite, walk-in closet, dual sinks and closet organizers.  Cozy Living area w/wood fireplace and a Newly built family room!  Open and Airy Eat in Kitchen has Stainless appliances and plenty of storage including a duel desk built-in.  Home sits on a huge lot with patio, raised gardens beds, a large dog run or parking for your toys and tools and plenty of privacy.  Oversized 2-car garage w/ tons of storage and a mini split air conditioning unit!!  Great schools, near shopping and only 15 minutes to the airport. Make an appointment to view today!
